<Root><Story><chapter>The Sunriders</chapter> <p1>The Sunriders philosophy is simple: glory through battle. This drives most of their life, from their transient dwellings to their ability to rapidly mobilize and advance against an enemy.</p1> <p1>The only elaborate and permanent dwellings are large structures to support the many farms, such as mills and tanneries. These are guarded by smaller garrisons inhabited by a mix of newly minted fighters and troops recently retired from the front lines. Defense isn’t a great concern of the Sunriders, since the vast tracts of land are so difficult to traverse.</p1> <p1>Horses make up a centerpiece of daily life. Huge, powerful destriers, from which the Sunriders get their name, are jealously protected and bred for use in battle and transport. Learning to ride and command them is started at a young age.</p1> <p1>There is only one leader, Arban the Swift, unquestionably the strongest and most powerful in battle. He delegates authority to a number of generals he trusts. Leadership changes tend to be bloody affairs for the Sunriders, as one group extends out and eliminates another.</p1> <p1>Magic is somewhat of a fascinating mystery to the Sunriders. They have a great interest in harnessing mana from the land, but besides lacking expertise, the lands they control are for the most part lacking in the energies found elsewhere.</p1> <h1>Features</h1> <p1>The Sunriders are geared for warfare, and their aspects and abilities reflect that.</p1> <h2>Aspects</h2> <ul><l1><aspect>Glory in Battle!</aspect></l1> <l1><aspect>Too many words! Not enough action!</aspect></l1> <l1><aspect>Might Makes Right</aspect></l1> <l1><aspect>A Bright and Wide Open Homeland</aspect></l1></ul> <h2>Common Names</h2> <ul><l1><b>Male </b>– Ganbayan, Unegei, Boladai, Qarader, Buqadai, Jebe, Altan, Bartan, Buri Boke, Taichu</l1> <l1><b>Female – </b>Shria, Enqela, Nasa, Altani, Amur, Hulan, Abagai, Alangoa, Chotan, Nomolun</l1></ul> <h2>Starting Attributes</h2> <ul><l1><b>Population: </b>15</l1> <l1><b>Stability: </b>5</l1></ul> <h2>Developments</h2> <ul><l1><b>Arcane: </b>None</l1> <l1><b>Diplomacy: </b>None</l1> <l1><b>Infiltration: </b>Great Spies</l1> <l1><b>Skirmish: </b>None</l1> <l1><b>Warfare: </b>Barracks, Great Barracks, Superb Barracks, Fletcher, Stables</l1></ul> <h1>Leaders</h1> <statblock><Table xmlns:aid="http://ns.adobe.com/AdobeInDesign/4.0/" aid:table="table" aid:trows="12" aid:tcols="2"><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>Arban the Swift</strong> </Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Type</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Leader</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Physical</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>4</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Mental</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>4</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Consequences</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">-2 <fate>1</fate> -4 <fate>1</fate> -6 <fate>1</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Superb (+5)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Tactics, Leadership</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Great (+4)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Fighting, Physique</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Good (+3)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Empathy, Will</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Decent (+2)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Athletics, Nature</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Average (+1)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Rapport, Society</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><aspect>Glorious Ruler of the Open Steppes</aspect> <aspect>Predictably Ruthless</aspect> <aspect>“Our weakness is our vulnerability to sorcery.”</aspect> <aspect>“Do not let fear guide you!”</aspect></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>TBD - </strong>TBD</Cell></Table></statblock> <p1>Arban looks first to war and conquest in solving any sort of resource issues, then to diplomacy. Fascinated by the power of the arcane.</p1> <statblock><Table xmlns:aid="http://ns.adobe.com/AdobeInDesign/4.0/" aid:table="table" aid:trows="12" aid:tcols="2"><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>Ganghal</strong> </Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Type</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Leader</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Physical</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>3</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Mental</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>3</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Consequences</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">-2 <fate>1</fate> -4 <fate>1</fate> -6 <fate>1</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Superb (+5)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Tactics, Empathy</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Great (+4)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Fighting, Leadership</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Good (+3)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Intimidation, Deceive</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Decent (+2)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Will, Nature</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Average (+1)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Stealth, Physique</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><aspect>Military Commander</aspect> <aspect>I Confide in Ile</aspect> <aspect>Unquestioning Loyalty to Arban</aspect> <aspect>“Speed is more important than power.”</aspect></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>TBD - </strong>TBD</Cell></Table></statblock> <p1>Arban’s chief commander for the Sunriders’ military.  Ganghal is primarily interested in military innovation.</p1> <statblock><Table xmlns:aid="http://ns.adobe.com/AdobeInDesign/4.0/" aid:table="table" aid:trows="12" aid:tcols="2"><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>Dashen</strong> </Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Type</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Leader</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Physical</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>4</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Mental</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>3</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Consequences</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">-2 <fate>1</fate> -4 <fate>1</fate> -6 <fate>1</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Superb (+5)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Rapport, Nature</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Great (+4)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Society, Channeling</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Good (+3)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Fighting, Physique</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Decent (+2)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Athletics, Will</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Average (+1)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Leadership, Empathy</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><aspect>Chief Horsemaster</aspect> <aspect>Youthful Naiveté</aspect> <aspect>“I hear our ancestors song.”</aspect> <aspect>“Our horses are the best in the Realm.”</aspect></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>TBD - </strong>TBD</Cell></Table></statblock> <p1>While Dashen doesn’t have much influence to speak of with Arbal, he is usually involved in outside deals, and may be used to raise issues regarding the protection and use of the Sunriders’ mounts.</p1> <statblock><Table xmlns:aid="http://ns.adobe.com/AdobeInDesign/4.0/" aid:table="table" aid:trows="12" aid:tcols="2"><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>Hogel</strong> </Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Type</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Leader</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Physical</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>4</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Mental</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>3</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Consequences</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">-2 <fate>1</fate> -4 <fate>1</fate> -6 <fate>1</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Superb (+5)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Society, Lore</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Great (+4)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Leadership, Empathy</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Good (+3)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Deceive, Physique</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Decent (+2)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Will, Rapport</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Average (+1)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Lore, Tactics</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><aspect>Lord of the Millet Plain</aspect> <aspect>Broker of Shrewd Deals</aspect> <aspect>Hotheaded Demagogue</aspect> <aspect>““You’re whining as much as a woman.”</aspect></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>TBD - </strong>TBD</Cell></Table></statblock> <p1>Hogel looks for opportunities to get ahead, although he is careful not to stoke Arban’s ire.</p1> <statblock><Table xmlns:aid="http://ns.adobe.com/AdobeInDesign/4.0/" aid:table="table" aid:trows="12" aid:tcols="2"><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>Ile</strong> </Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Type</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Leader</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Physical</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>2</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Mental</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002"><fate>4</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Consequences</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">-2 <fate>1</fate> -2 <fate>1</fate> -4 <fate>1</fate> -6 <fate>1</fate></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Superb (+5)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Will, Society</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Great (+4)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Lore, Leadership</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Good (+3)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Rapport, Channeling</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Decent (+2)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Nature, Athletics</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="88.29999999999998"><b>Average (+1)</b></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="1" aid:ccolwidth="174.70000000000002">Science, Tactics</Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><aspect>Kidnapped Speaker from Moonrider Clan</aspect> <aspect>Keeper of Ancient Lore</aspect> <aspect>“I have come to expect a great deal of pain in this life.”</aspect> <aspect>“Show respect when you speak to me.”</aspect></Cell><Cell aid:table="cell" aid:crows="1" aid:ccols="2"><strong>TBD - </strong>TBD</Cell></Table></statblock> <p1>Ile has accepted her tragic lot in life, and now looks to carve out a niche for herself within the Sunriders clan. She understands magical better than most of the Sunriders.</p1> <h1>Diplomacy</h1> <p1>Ultimately, Arban decides the fate of the Sunriders.  Practically speaking, responsibility is delegated among other leaders.</p1> <h2>Trade Chart</h2> <tableblock><Table xmlns:aid="http://ns.adobe.com/AdobeInDesign/4